<p>I need to make a website multilingual. For this, I'll extract a lot of strings from multiple HTML files to add it to a json ressource file.</p>  <p>So, if a have :</p>  <pre><code>&lt;strong&gt;Hello World&lt;/strong&gt; </code></pre>  <p>I would like a tool so I can just select "Hello World" and get this :</p>  <pre><code>&lt;strong&gt;{{translation.hello_world}}&lt;/strong&gt; </code></pre>  <p>And add to a single ressource json file</p>  <pre><code>{       "hello_world" : "Hello World",       ...              } </code></pre>  <p><em>Note : I tried macros with no luck, as they can't work on multiple files...</em></p>